schemas.name: schema.graphql
schemas.content:
type Query {
  stories(type: StoryType!, page: Int!, count: Int!): [Story]
  items(ids: [Int]): [Item]
  user(id: ID!): User
}

enum StoryType {
  top
  new
  best
  ask
  show
  job
}

type Story {
  id: ID!
  descendants: Int
  kids: [Int]
  score: Int
  time: Int
  text: String
  title: String
  type: String
  url: String
  by: String
}

type Item {
  id: ID!
  descendants: Int
  kids: [Int]
  kidsItems: [Item]
  score: Int
  time: Int
  text: String
  title: String
  type: String
  url: String
  by: String
}

type User {
  id: ID!
  about: String
  created: Int
  karma: Int
}
